label.value: prevalence of wild type Cyp4J5 L43

definition.value: A data item that is the output of an assay to quantify the frequency of the reference sequence amino acid at Cyp4J5 L43 or is calculated from data items of the frequency of a variant at that position.

label.value: date of start of process resulting in collection of specimens

definition.value: A time measurement datum that specifies the date that starts a process that results in a collection of specimens.

label.value: date of end of process resulting in collection of specimens

definition.value: A time measurement datum that specifies the date that ends a process that results in a collection of specimens.

label.value: indicator of specimen collection date discontinuity

definition.value: An information content entity that specifies that, between the start and end dates of a process resulting in a collection of specimens, there was at least one date that no collection attempts were made.
An information content entity that is about a population of tick specimens.

label.value: no record of collected tick population

definition.value: A record of missing knowledge indicating a lack of information on collected tick population.

label.value: reported information on collected tick population

definition.value: An information on collected tick population that does not meet the criteria for established information on collected tick population, but indicates that at least one tick (or an unspecified number of ticks) of any life stage had been identified at any time in a second-order administrative region.

label.value: established information on collected tick population

definition.value: An information on collected tick population that indicates that at least six individual ticks or at least two of the three host-seeking life stages had been identified in a single collection period in a second-order administrative region.

label.value: umbilical cord blood specimen collection process

definition.value: A collecting specimen from organism that has the objective to obtain an umbilical cord blood specimen.
A blood assay datum of the concentration of hydroxychloroquine.

label.value: presence of Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 in nasopharynx or oropharynx by real time reverse-transcription polymerase chain reaction assay

definition.value: A virus in nasopharyngeal or oropharyngeal swab datum that specifies whether severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 was detected by real time reverse-transcription polymerase chain reaction assay.
A second-order administrative region of Uganda.
